        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51711",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=frosch",
                        "name": "frosch",
                        "displayName": "Frank Br\u00fcckner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "There is a problem:\r\n{code}\r\n$element = new Zend_Form_Element_Text('foo');\r\n$element->setDecorators(array('ViewHelper', 'Label');\r\n\r\n$form->addElement($element);\r\n{code}\r\nIf we add the element decorators from the form, then we override the current decorators of the element. Bad idea!\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=frosch",
                        "name": "frosch",
                        "displayName": "Frank Br\u00fcckner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-08-24T17:10:37.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-08-24T17:10:37.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51722",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=samadams83",
                        "name": "samadams83",
                        "displayName": "Sam Adams",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I agree that explicitly set decorators should take precedence over the form element defaults, but it makes sense to be able to change the default set of decorators that are used for elements without explicitly set decorators. The alternative is (if you want to use the object method) to add the decorators to each element every time, which is wasteful.\r\nIs there a way of inspecting the element object to see if decorators were set, and if not, set the form default?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=samadams83",
                        "name": "samadams83",
                        "displayName": "Sam Adams",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-08-25T16:13:35.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-08-25T16:13:35.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51807",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=shamseerss",
                        "name": "shamseerss",
                        "displayName": "shamseer",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "when an element is created by this code\r\n$el = new Zend_Form_Element_Text('foo'); \r\n\r\ndefault decorators(ViewHelper, Errors,....) added by default, if decorator option is not specified in the constructor.\r\n\r\nBetter to create your own factory for elements creation\r\n\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=shamseerss",
                        "name": "shamseerss",
                        "displayName": "shamseer",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-09-05T12:51:23.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-09-05T12:51:23.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51810",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=frosch",
                        "name": "frosch",
                        "displayName": "Frank Br\u00fcckner",
